{"type": "article", "id": 28352, "title": "露华浓收购雅顿，以及，H&M 又推出高端运动系列｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-06-17T11:35:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29106, "name": "LVMH 大奖赛"}, {"id": 1241, "name": "男装"}, {"id": 862, "name": "设计师"}, {"id": 664, "name": "投资"}, {"id": 393, "name": "收购"}, {"id": 4536, "name": "护肤品"}, {"id": 1936, "name": "香水"}, {"id": 1027, "name": "彩妆"}, {"id": 3786, "name": "包袋"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 13154, "name": "露华浓"}, {"id": 12940, "name": "雅顿"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 12783, "name": "平安"}, {"id": 22261, "name": "Revlon"}, {"id": 15558, "name": "Vince"}, {"id": 1612, "name": "Mac"}, {"id": 14105, "name": "porter"}, {"id": 3321, "name": "Stella McCartney"}, {"id": 29107, "name": "Ariana Grand"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703122328VspJxIkPtldzOov1.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/6/16/11952672/stella-mccartney-mens-clothes\"><b>Stella McCartney 确认推出男装</b></a>｜WWD 曾在二月报道过“据传” 女装设计师  Stella McCartney 将发布男装系列（于 2017 春季）。近日纽约时报首次证实了这一传闻，Stella McCartney 的男装线将包括男士服装及配饰，她<a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/6/16/11958890/revlon-elizabeth-arden\">更向 Racked 证实</a>品牌预计于 11 月 10 日在伦敦发布，12 月在门店上市。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/6/16/11958890/revlon-elizabeth-arden\"><b>露华浓收购雅顿</b></a>｜露华浓（Revlon）以 8.7 亿美元收购了伊丽莎白·雅顿（Elizabeth Arden），后者于 1910 年创立，目前在 120 个国家有售，在护肤品类尤其是抗皱产品方面见长，还拥有与 Britney Spears、Justin Bieber、Taylor Swift 等名人授权的香水业务。而露华浓主要业务在于美发、彩妆。此次是本月美妆领域内第二大规模的收购，仅次于资生堂收购 Laura Mercier 和 RéVive。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Vince-appoints-new-senior-VP-of-retail-and-VP-brand-director,702943.html\"><b>Vince 任命新高管</b></a>｜时装品牌 Vince 宣布任命 Terence Bogan 为零售部门高级副总裁、Tomoko Ogura 为副总裁兼品牌总监。其中，Bogan 将监管包括商品分类、店铺运营和视觉陈列等零售业务，Ogura 则将掌管市场、公关及创意团队。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/grace-wales-bonner-lvmh-prize-2016-winner\"><b>LVMH 大奖赛冠军揭晓</b></a>｜周四，伦敦男女装设计师 Grace Wales Bonner 在巴黎获得了本届 LVMH 大奖赛冠军，成 LVMH 第一位获奖的男装设计师，她将获得 30 万欧元的奖金，以及为期 12 个月对其品牌 Wales Bonner 的技术、财政支持。2014 年毕业于中央圣马丁（Central Saint Martins） 后，2015 年获得了英国时装协会颁发的新兴男装设计师奖。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/financial/nu-skin-plans-china-expansion-with-210-million-investment-10457788/\"><b>如新获平安证券 2.1 亿美元投资</b></a>｜美国美容及营养品直销公司如新（Nu Skin）获得中国平安证券牵头的财团投资 2.1 亿美元，此举有助于集团在中国的进一步扩张。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p>H&amp;M 推出<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/hm-high-fashion-performance-sportswear\">高端运动系列 “For Every Victory”</a>，设计过程中与瑞典奥运队，采用快干、透气面料，强调技术、性能及时尚的结合。7 月 21 日在 H&amp;M 门店上市。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122317ULOqj3fwtr28dkPy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031223174Uh5Y3yAm7ZuIJeW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031223181pUCViNF4b5e9ukh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122319tWrjXvSVZLbiaHzs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122319CHJMc7LQxpvZG1eb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/salvatore-ferragamo-2016-fall-collection\">Salvatore Ferragamo 秋季运动鞋系列</a>不错：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122319jfpLbTs4HUdltV05.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070312232080erIEOumpS5clUL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031223204yPEnVovc0j31DKM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122321V6Tegodk7KlFYbDL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031223212BcpPd7uH54q96XJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p>一向展现波西米亚风情的 Free People，旗下<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/free-people-movement-activewear-no-restrictions/\">运动线 FP Movement 发布新品</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122322wS8cZ5HdgQYhjKVb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.465\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122322NAPtblWTSJe7f02d.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122323E7A61GFuk4NxvUCX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122323u3JCkHeU1GNp8KTn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">旧金山科技公司  Chronicled 与 Mache Custom Kicks 合作，在父亲节即将来临之际，为 Kanye West 和他的女儿  North 推出了一个  <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/kanye-west-fathers-day-ultra-boost\">Ultra Boosts 特别系列的球鞋</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122323iJTZXfL9cUwdo3Ye.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122324hKDpQVlyFwWBzYEa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122324tpR1OXNvgBlbukhr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122325PBSFQCo9ip38zGca.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>创造了经典形象“史努比”的花生漫画（Peanuts）此前和包袋品牌 PORTER 推出过一个简单的联名系列，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/6/porter-peanuts-collaboration-accessories\">此次再度合作</a>，将推出行李袋、腰包、钱包、双肩包等：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122325YbhxABd90kMPUTEl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66750314\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122326NMu2n0epXHscUt8A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748466\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031223266ItfpnEePk9oYDqH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66829268\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122327k7nFdpRfDsWIKP6o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122327OG3Y8VXxsEpBtUZD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p>流行歌手 Ariana Grande 宣布与彩妆品牌 MAC 的<a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/6/16/11954016/ariana-grande-MAC-second-collection\">第二次合作将于九月上市</a>。紫色系唇彩：</p>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703122327BDoucWCzNaMqiV9H.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070312232889rxGzJQT1sw2egb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"medium-insert-images-wide\"><br></p>\n\n"}